 (ii) Telnet Configuration on Router
1.Configure enable password or enable secret password on the router
Router>en
Router#config term
Router(config)#enable password admin

2.Configure IP addresses on the admin PC and interface fa0/0 of the router
Router(config)#int fa0/0
Router(config-if)#ip adress 10.0.0.1  255.0.0.0
Router(config-if)#no shut

3.Configure VLAN interface on the router.This interface allows for remote access on a switch or router via protocols such as Telnet or Secure Shell (SSH)
Router(config)#int VLAN1
Router(config-if)#no shutdown
